Class Jam

  • java.lang.Object
    • Jam

  • public class Jam
extends java.lang.Object
    This program imitates a pantry containing three jars of jam It allows you to fill it with your flavors of jam and remove a certain amount of jam. It also checks for empty jam jars.

    Dhruv
